{"_id":"1N0uxbeCtDTXyYHz","name":"Signal Cable","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>This gadget is a cable of medium length (100 feet + 10 feet per rank in Craft (mechanical)). As a swift action, you can link one end of the cable to either another end of a separate cable within reach or to a gadget of your creation (un-linking the cable is another swift action). Gadgets (including cables) can have any number of other cables linked.</p>\n<p>Taking a linked gadget beyond medium range of another gadget requires a Strength check opposed by your Tech sphere DC. Success un-links the cables, failure means you cannot take the gadget farther than this distance. Gadgets linked by this cable are considered to be within signal distance of each other regardless of their actual distance and intervening materials, or jammed signals, even if they do not normally possess a signal otherwise. Whenever a gadget would consume a charge, it can instead consume a charge from a separate gadget linked to it by signal cable.</p>\n<p>You can create a number of signal cables equal to your practitioner modifier as one gadget, and they count as one gadget for the purpose of the amount of gadgets you may maintain at once.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Gadget"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Tech","identifiedName":"Signal Cable"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.DK9lfabEwzeKonmd"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereTech"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"1Qcgi3a3ooguhGD6","name":"Draining Despair","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Gladiator sphere.</p>\n<p>While in this stance, whenever a creature demoralized by you misses you with an attack roll, they must succeed at a Will save or take nonlethal damage equal to your ranks in Intimidate. An individual creature may only take damage from draining despair once per round.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Demoralization"],["Stance"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Gladiator","identifiedName":"Draining Despair"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.rFVdSM4eawADZ5yY"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereGladiator"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/gladiator.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"1TD3kwNI2Tj7Yp2a","name":"Allied Cover","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>When you are within your cohort&#8217;s threatened area, you gain a 20% miss chance against attacks the cohort is aware of. The benefits from multiple cohorts do not stack.</p>\n<p>When you are targeted by an attack or single-target effect and are within the threatened area of a cohort, you may expend martial focus to redirect the attack or effect to the cohort as a joint immediate action.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Cohort"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Leadership","identifiedName":"Allied Cover"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.vjUpdHAIrm2CyCVT"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereLeadership"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"1YZE0IeuefBQSrwV","name":"Defensive Teamwork","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>While within the threatened area of an animal ally, when you or the animal ally is targeted by an attack, the other may make an aid another check to boost AC as an immediate action.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Beastmastery","identifiedName":"Defensive Teamwork"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.M1xRwdrcfd0fPkMn"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereBeastmastery"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/beastmastery.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"1cGKHWHJpKRa9TGh","name":"Slickened Grip","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You aim your attacks for delicate veins whose bleeding causes the creature&#8217;s grasp to become slick and uncertain. When you deal bleed damage to a creature, they take a penalty to CMD equal to the total amount of bleed damage they are currently taking vs disarm and sunder attempts. This penalty is halved vs all other maneuvers (minimum: 1).</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Bleed"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Duelist","identifiedName":"Slickened Grip"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.J0b0mC1NP6x7ETL2"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereDuelist"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/duelist.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"1dfD4dy2Ys7E6QSF","name":"Unsettling Visage","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your excessive brutality is unnerving, and makes your enemies uneasy around you. Until the end of your next turn, you may spend an attack of opportunity to attempt an Intimidate check to demoralize an opponent within range of this boast that targets you with an attack, including a targeted spell. You may expend your martial focus to attempt this Intimidate check in place of spending an attack of opportunity. You may not use this talent in conjunction with Frightful or any other ability that would allow you to use the Intimidate skill to demoralize beyond the shaken condition.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Boast"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Gladiator","identifiedName":"Unsettling Visage"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.RU7qDOerMmrbC4jP"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresShee