{"_id":"78h5vtWOgN2moCbw","name":"Push Shot","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>On a successful deadly shot, you may make a free ranged bull rush attempt against the target, using your original attack roll for the deadly shot as your combat maneuver check. You do not need to move to push the target, nor do you provoke an attack of opportunity for this combat maneuver, except as usual when making ranged attacks.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Snipe"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Sniper","identifiedName":"Push Shot"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.aLR3nWlQH4MxzJfH"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereSniper"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/sniper.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"78vw9jer3Sh0rtQB","name":"Last Chance Grapple","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Whenever you attempt to initiate a grapple as a standard action and fail, you may expend your martial focus to make another grapple attempt against the same creature as a swift action without provoking an attack of opportunity.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Wrestling","identifiedName":"Last Chance Grapple"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.EbCy1HdTjBS5cwMN"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereWrestling"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/wrestling.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"7AQd3tC1BuobXTfK","name":"Expert Feint","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>When you succeed at a feint check against a target, that target also loses its Dexterity bonus to its armor class against all attacks until the beginning of your next turn, in addition to your next attack. <strong>Associated Feat:</strong> Greater Feint.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Fencing","identifiedName":"Expert Feint"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.K1aleAJho366hASe"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereFencing"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/fencing.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"7C87tN0SAggp8zUQ","name":"External Health Modulator","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>When activated with 1 or more charges, the attached creature gains a +2 enhancement bonus to Constitution. The modulator use up 1 charge per minute of use. This bonus to Constitution increases by +2 per 7 ranks in Craft (mechanical). The External Health Modulator occupies the body slot. Failing a Fortitude save against remote control makes you nauseated for 1 round. Creatures without Constitution scores wearing this active augment instead gain 1 temporary hit point per Hit Dice, plus an additional hit point per Hit Dice per 7 ranks in Craft (mechanical).</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Augment"],["Drone"],["Gadget"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Tech","identifiedName":"External Health Modulator"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.TfrSpz0kqJ22M2lR"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":