{"_id":"7CZ4qI2exqY4byqD","name":"Double Dip","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Whenever you successfully perform a dirty trick combat maneuver, you may expend your martial focus as a free action to select two different conditions to apply to a creature instead of just one, although both conditions may be removed with the same action. When you have at least 10 ranks in Sleight of Hand, you can instead apply up to three conditions. You cannot use this talent to apply conditions that could not normally be applied by a dirty trick (such as with the savage dirty trick rage power).</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Trick"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Scoundrel","identifiedName":"Double Dip"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.lPMRLkiS8pf0X4K8"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereScoundrel"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/scoundrel.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"7NV0elIf3NUbwNYw","name":"Cooperative Clothesline","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Whenever you fail a trip combat maneuver against an enemy threatened by an ally, as an immediate action the ally may attempt a trip attempt against the enemy. This does not provoke attacks of opportunity.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Open Hand","identifiedName":"Cooperative Clothesline"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.oxa250Dvy4lLvdLE"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereOpenHand"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/open_hand.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"7OOS9JBX6XNowntw","name":"Superior Joints","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>This gadget integrates with armor to make it less cumbersome and more efficient. The armor&#8217;s maximum Dexterity bonus is increased by 1, and the armor&#8217;s armor check penalty is reduced by 3. These bonuses increase by 1 for every 6 ranks in Craft (mechanical) you possess. This accessory consumes 1 charge per hour in use.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Gadget"],["Accessory"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Tech","identifiedName":"Superior Joints"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.j3Jxf3GTAX9mMLl1"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereTech"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"7TOKzxbu35DpBFNB","name":"Small Arms","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You do not take penalties for using weapons sized for smaller creatures. For example, a Medium creature could wield a two-handed weapon sized for smaller creatures in one hand without incurring the penalty for wielding inappropriately sized weapons.</p>\n<p>Additionally, you gain a cumulative +1 bonus to Sleight of Hand checks made to conceal a weapon on your person for each size smaller the weapon is sized for. For example, a Medium creature using a dagger sized for Tiny creatures would receive a +2 bonus to a Sleight of Hand check to conceal it on their person.</p>\n<p><strong>Normal:</strong> Using a weapon inappropriately sized for you incurs a -2 penalty on attack rolls for each size category difference. A weapon smaller than its wielder takes one step less effort to wield in combat for each step smaller they are than the wielder. A Small-sized two-handed weapon can be wielded by a Medium creature as a one-handed weapon. A Small-sized one-handed weapon can be wielded by a Medium creature as a light weapon. See the weapon rules for more details (Pathfinder Roleplaying Game Core Rulebook pg. 140).</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Equipment","identifiedName":"Small Arms"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.lmpPAMpRd8jvN7J7"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereEquipment"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/equipment.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"7UObweQkXcUqeUVH","name":"Improved Liquid Nice","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Craft DC:</strong> 10</p>\n<p>You create a flask of pleasant thought distillate that functions as a splash weapon you can use as a ranged touch attack with a range increment of 10 feet. Anyone standing in the square of impact or adjacent squares must attempt Will saves. Creatures who fail their saving throw have their disposition toward you increased by 1 step to a maximum of friendly for 1 minute per rank in Craft (alchemy). This is a mind-affecting compulsion effect.</p>\n<p>You can increase the Craft DC for this weapon in increments of 10; each time you do so, the radius increases by 5 feet. You can separately increase the Craft DC for this weapon by an increment of 20 to increase its potency; when you do so, any creature who fails its Will save against this effect instead have their disposition towards you increase to friendly for the duration.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Formulae"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges