{"_id":"7hh6qJWDZvzBNaGz","name":"Synaptic Reaction Maximizer","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>When activated with 1 or more charges, the attached creature gains a +2 enhancement bonus to Dexterity. The maximizer use up 1 charge per minute of use. This bonus to Dexterity increases by +2 per 7 ranks in Craft (mechanical). The reaction maximizer occupies the brain slot. Failing a Reflex save against remote control makes you paralyzed for 1 round.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Augment"],["Drone"],["Gadget"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Tech","identifiedName":"Synaptic Reaction Maximizer"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.uUTjc7OA3PEeQZ2P"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereTech"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"7m9LK8RyBsaQ9FHM","name":"Trapped Shield","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You may place Trap sphere dart traps onto any shield (except a buckler) you&#8217;re wielding using a normal placement action. Whenever you are missed by a melee attack, you may trigger the trap as an immediate action, making the trap&#8217;s attack against the attacking creature. If you possess the Shield sphere, you may instead trigger the trap as a (deflect) ability.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Trap","identifiedName":"Trapped Shield"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.0HaCpDbgD3WOJtL7"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereTrap"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/trap.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"7rEkJ5E5nvGSuDgA","name":"Enthusiastic Cheer","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>One allied creature within range gains a number of temporary hit points equal to your Intimidate ranks (minimum 1). These temporary hit points last for 1 minute. For every 4 ranks in Intimidate you possess, you may affect an additional ally.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Boast"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Gladiator","identifiedName":"Enthusiastic Cheer"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.vGAc7pzHPXDNwdhY"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereGladiator"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/gladiator.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"82zTTpVJzHlBkmU3","name":"Auto Injector","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You create an auto injector. This gadget can inject 1 potion or potion-like substance (such as formulae from the Alchemy sphere) into the user as a swift action without provoking attacks of opportunity using up 1 charge to do so. For every additional 10 ranks of Craft (mechanical) the auto injector can store an additional potion. It occupies any 1 slot of choice. Inserting or removing a potion from an auto injector requires a minute. If used in conjunction with the Evac Pack, the Evac Pack will activate the auto injector after withdrawing. Failing a Fortitude save against remote control allows the controller to inject a potion stored in the auto injector into you.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Augment"],["Gadget"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Tech","identifiedName":"Auto Injector"},"