{"_id":"pPzq790tMeLHU3EA","name":"Unstoppable","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>When making a charge, you can push your way through obstacles blocking your path, be they creatures, objects, or others.</p>\n<p>You may charge over difficult terrain. This movement still costs twice as much as normal. Additionally, when making a charge, you may attempt to overrun a creature in the path of the charge, or to make a Strength check to break an unattended object such as a door or wall that is in your way, as a free action that does not provoke an attack of opportunity. If the check is successful, you may complete the charge. If the check is unsuccessful, the charge ends in the space directly in front of that creature or object.</p>\n<p>For every 5 base attack bonus you possess you may attempt to break or overrun an additional target, but suffer a cumulative -2 penalty on each additional check made.</p>\n<p>This can allow you to initiate a charge through squares that you do not have line of sight to. You may resolve your charge attack against any valid target within reach of the charge&#8217;s path after passing through the barriers (creature or object) blocking your line of sight. <strong>Associated Feat:</strong> Charge Through.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Brute","identifiedName":"Unstoppable"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.EMpzuyVsm1VvNsux"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereBrute"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/brute.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"pRgyfER5WiNFbK8x","name":"Wind Reader","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You can use your trained senses to read the movements of the wind and other factors in the environment to improve your accuracy with ranged attacks. As long as you have martial focus, you may spend a swift action to halve the penalties to ranged attacks inflicted by wind, rain, or other weather in regard to your next ranged attack, made before the end of your turn.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Scout","identifiedName":"Wind Reader"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.rk0MQBOsm3tA8d62"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereScout"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/scout.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"pVnywvSVWVjsYuZV","name":"Painter","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You can apply an additional war paint to yourself, plus an additional paint for each 7 ranks in Craft (alchemy) you possess. Applying the same war paint color to yourself more than once does not increase the benefits granted.</p>\n<p><strong>Normal:</strong> You can only have one war paint color active at a time.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Alchemy","identifiedName":"Painter"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.d3kjqghpVk5eQ6S6"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereAlchemy"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/alchemy.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"pWGw2ZOLuDIkPPiR","name":"Overhead Flip","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>As part of an attack action, you may roll an Acrobatics check to jump against the CMD of any adjacent creature. If your roll exceeds their CMD, you may jump to any other square adjacent to that creature that would enable flanking with your starting position without provoking an attack of opportunity for movement, and you may treat the creature as flanked by you for the attack action. If unsuccessful, you instead provoke an attack of opportunity from the targeted creature and do not complete your movement.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Leap"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Athletics","identifiedName":"Overhead Flip"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.LLZHtuWFLpZrWnMo"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereAthletics"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/athletics.png","e