{"_id":"rtUe7YGjDv4gQVX1","name":"Inimical Gaze","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Scout sphere, Perception 5 ranks.</p>\n<p>The scout ability granted by the Scout sphere is now a gaze attack that can affect any creature within 60 ft. You may activate this gaze as a free action and it stays active until the end of your next turn. Any creature subject to the gaze that fails a Will save is automatically scouted by you.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Scout","identifiedName":"Inimical Gaze"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.USmCsVCDeo4mgBqZ"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereScout"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/scout.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"rvbjGfsoDKvDAHQp","name":"Swinging Swap","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Whenever you make a successful unarmed strike against a creature using the attack action, you can swap positions with that creature (creatures larger than you must end this talent&#8217;s movement occupying at least one space that you did, allowing them to choose their exact position). If you successfully use this talent on the same creature during two consecutive rounds, that creature must make a successful Will saving throw or be confused for 1 round.</p>\n<p>At +10 base attack bonus, the duration of this confusion increases to a number of rounds equal to your practitioner modifier, although the creature can make an additional save at the beginning of each of its turns with a -2 penalty; this penalty increases by -2 each time you successfully use this talent against it while it is suffering the effects of this talent.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Open Hand","identifiedName":"Swinging Swap"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ZmvPqDK6vqwVASwL"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereOpenHand"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/open_hand.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"rwCWRILjcgMCmu7P","name":"Hard Landing","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Whenever you successfully trip a creature, they become battered for one round. Additionally, you always treat prone creatures within reach as being battered for the purposes of talents and class abilities, and they cannot perform attacks of opportunity against you for performing combat maneuvers as long as they remain prone.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Open Hand","identifiedName":"Hard Landing"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.QqpTY3dTOZWAsSoJ"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereOpenHand"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/open_hand.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"rwgtQsajmKLg8oV2","name":"Trap Launcher","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You&#8217;re capable of setting traps at a distance. When placing a trap with a creation time of a standard action or less, you may increase the DC to create the trap by 10 in order to place the trap within the first range increment of a ranged weapon you are wielding. This is considered a ranged attack and as such provokes attacks of opportunity and is subject to conditions that affect ranged attacks (such as wind).</p>\n<p>If you possess the Sniper sphere, treat this talent as a (snipe) talent that allows you to shoot your traps directly at creatures.</p>\n<p>As part of a deadly shot, you create a snare trap that requires a standard action or less to create and fire it (this ignores the limitation of placing traps only within the first range increment of the weapon). A creature hit by the attack makes a Reflex save as normal to prevent triggering the snare, as if the snare trap originated from their square. As the trap is never set, creatures do not gain any bonus to AC or saves for seeing you set the trap. If a trap would usually activate multiple times, it only activates once. If the attack misses, the trap is destroyed.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Trap","identifiedName":"Trap Launcher"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.996ukYagVFVBsIo5"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereTrap"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/trap.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"rzIE5mVeolvOPbeh","name":"Disarming Jab","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Whenever you successfully attack with your counter punch, you can make a disarm attempt against the target as a free action which does not provoke attacks of opportunity. If you successfully disarm the target, you may automatically pick up the item dropped if you have an empty hand, even if you used a weapon to disarm the target.</p>\n<p>In addition, you gain the following new triggers to choose from when you ready a counter punch:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A hostile creature uses a consumable item (e.g. a potion, Alchemy sphere formulae, etc.)</li>\n<li>A hostile creature activates a magic item (e.g. a wand, spell engine, etc.)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Normal:</strong> When you successfully disarm your opponent without using a weapon, you may automatically pick up the item dropped.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Counter"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Boxing","identifiedName":"Disarming Jab"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.OiSerGgDzTY6luwE"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereBoxing"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/boxing.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"rzqgHbvcviyNrEus","name":"Focusing Connection","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You may make physical contact with one animal ally within your natural reach as a move action, regaining your martial focus and giving that animal ally a +1 bonus to all saving throws for 1 round. At 10 ranks in Handle Animal or Ride, this bonus increases to +2.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Beastmastery","identifiedName":"Focusing Connection"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ILoOfyg6eUiYSa5B"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereBeastmastery"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/beastmastery.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"s0G5NFQ7bIWQnu63","name":"Couriers Dash","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>All allies that start their turn within the radius of this tactic gain a +5 ft enhancement bonus to their base land speed. An ally who begins or ends their turn outside of this tactic&#8217;s affected area loses its benefits until they once more start their turn within its radius. For every 5 ranks in Diplomacy you possess, this enhancement bonus is increased by an additional 5 ft.</p>\n<p><strong>Addendum [Conq. HB]:</strong> You may take this talent twice. If taken a second time, instead of granting an enhancement bonus to base land speed, you may allow allies benefiting from this tactic to move through 5 feet of difficult terrain as if it were normal terrain, increasing by 5 feet for every 10 ranks of Diplomacy you possess, and allows allies to take a 5-foot step into difficult terrain.</p>\n<p><strong>Associated Feat:</strong> Nimble Moves (if taken twice).</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Tactic"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Warleader","identifiedName":"Couriers Dash"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.lXK6G1YxEpSiyrjG"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereWarleader"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/warleader.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"s0wV1PrY3tUDf9B0","name":"Marauder","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your body pushes itself further, allowing you to move faster than you normally could. You gain a +5 feet circumstance bonus on all forms of movement (such as land, climb, burrow, fly, or swim), increasing by +5 feet for every 4 points of base attack bonus you have. In addition, you gain a competence bonus on all Acrobatics, Climb, Fly, and Swim checks equal to half your base attack bonus (minimum 1).</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Adrenaline"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Berserker","identifiedName":"Marauder"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.rvLAaSStyw2nI0gY"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereBerserker"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/berserker.png","effects":[]}
