{"_id":"v6wQ6CmMIw56rPdR","name":"Habit Forming","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You can imbue poisons you create with the Alchemy sphere with highly addictive qualities. Whenever a creature fails a saving throw against your Alchemy sphere poison, it must attempt a Fortitude saving throw. On a failed saving throw, the creature develops an addiction to that poison. Creatures who fail their saving throw gain a minor addiction, which increases to moderate and severe with additional subsequent failed saving throws against this talent. Penalties from this addiction begin 24 hours after first becoming addicted.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A minor addiction causes the creature to suffer a -2 penalty to Constitution.</li>\n<li>A moderate addiction increases this penalty to -4 to Strength and Constitution.</li>\n<li>A severe addiction increases this penalty to -6 to Strength, Dexterity, and Constitution.These penalties are suppressed for 24 hours whenever the creature fails a saving throw against the poison.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Each day the creature does not fail a saving throw against your Alchemy sphere poisons, it may attempt a Fortitude save against your Alchemy sphere DC. After succeeding at a save in this fashion, the DC is reduced by 2. If it succeeds at 2 consecutive saves, its addiction also reduces by one level (or disappears, if it only has a minor addiction).</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Alchemy","identifiedName":"Habit Forming"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.j1IDsfWSazJB3Zi7"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereAlchemy"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/alchemy.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"vHHF3ZATax18dxOJ","name":"Discern Tells","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You gain a competence bonus to your Sense Motive checks equal to 1/2 your ranks in Perception (minimum 1) against any creature you have successfully scouted. Training in this talent allows you to use Sense Motive to resist a Bluff attempt to feint if desired, even if you are not trained in Sense Motive.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Scout","identifiedName":"Discern Tells"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.kVAmN6vNnhkgCtAA"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereScout"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/scout.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"vHlevBggNt5nwAos","name":"Healers","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your followers include healers. They can supply you with one complete healer&#8217;s kit each day, increasing by 1 additional kit for every 5 ranks in Diplomacy that you possess. These healers kits cannot be sold or stockpiled. These healers can treat wounds as you rest, restoring 10 hit points per rank in Diplomacy to a number of creatures equal to your practitioner modifier (minimum 1) over 8 hours of rest.</p>\n<p>Any Heal checks made while with the followers automatically gain a +2 circumstance bonus from the healers&#8217; aid. This bonus increases by +1 for every 8 ranks in Diplomacy that you possess.</p>\n<p>If you possess the Messengers talent, your messengers can carry wounded allies to your followers or caravan or can administer limited healing. This limited healing requires 10 minutes and restores up to 2 hit points per rank in Diplomacy. A creature may only benefit from this healing a number of times per day equal to your practitioner modifier.</p>\n<p>If you possess the (cohort) package, your cohorts begin each day with a complete healer&#8217;s kit. These kits cannot be sold or stockpiled.</p>\n<p>If using the Downtime rules from Ultimate Campaign, your followers may generate Influence or Magic capital in place of earning gold, with 15 gp equalling 1 Influence or 50 gp equaling 1 Magic. Use your Diplomacy modifier for making the earnings checks. This stacks with capital gains from other talents.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Followers"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Leadership","identifiedName":"Healers"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.HgPOglOikIU6USft"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereLeadership"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"vL0rLdS1zdm4yJyQ","name":"Sparrows Path","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Athletics sphere, Fly 3 ranks.</p>\n<p>You gain a fly speed equal to half your base speed, with a maneuverability of clumsy. The fly speed only functions during your turn; if you are not on a surface that can support you at the end of your turn, you fall. If you deal damage to a hostile creature with a melee attack during your turn, you may choose not to fall at the end of that turn.</p>\n<p>At 8 ranks in Fly, this fly speed becomes permanent. This is a supernatural effect.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Fly"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Athletics","identifiedName":"Sparrows Path"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.sW1Xj55CDoCfd1yF"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereAthletics"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/athletics.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"vaYdW8rXnABkNUlt","name":"Switcheroo","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Whenever you successfully perform a steal combat maneuver, you may replace what you stole with a different item, placing it in either an empty hand or pocket of the creature. If the item you placed on their person is somehow volatile (such as a vial of alchemist&#8217;s fire, a thunderstone, or an alchemist&#8217;s bomb), you can rig that item to explode as an immediate action (you must choose when to make the item explode within a number of rounds equal to your ranks in Sleight of Hand); you are immune to any damage or effects of explosions triggered in this manner. When you have at least 10 ranks in Sleight of Hand, you may choose when to make the item explode within a number of minutes equal to your ranks in Sleight of Hand.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"S