{"_id":"xTVqkoKO0Bgf48uH","name":"Air Cannon","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Open Hand sphere, base attack bonus +5.</p>\n<p>You can make unarmed strikes with such force that it creates howling winds. As a standard action, you may expend your martial focus to create a cone of air. This deals bludgeoning damage equal to twice your base unarmed strike damage die to all creatures within a close range cone (25 ft. + 5 ft. per 2 base attack bonus). Targets are allowed a Reflex save for half damage.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Open Hand","identifiedName":"Air Cannon"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.FzmUdbb0GYuhbaCp"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereOpenHand"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/open_hand.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"xVdFmUZEYnIDz2yf","name":"Prowess","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You may roll the next weapon attack you make before the end of your next turn twice and take the better result.</p>\n<h2 id=\"toc2\"><span><span style=\"color: #993300\">Demoralization</span></span></h2>\n<p>Some talents in this sphere have effects that allow new ways to make Intimidate skill checks to demoralize enemies or grant new options against demoralized foes. These talents carry the (demoralization) descriptor. When you gain the Gladiator sphere, you learn the following (demoralization) ability:</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Boast"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Gladiator","identifiedName":"Prowess"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.zPIjSSmbWarRaAT9"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereGladiator"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/gladiator.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"xWJees1peMSGQ9dg","name":"Blooded Skeptic","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Feint attempts made by creatures taking bleed damage always provoke attacks of opportunity from you, even if they would not normally do so. In addition, you gain a +1 competence bonus to Sense Motive checks, plus an additional +1 at base attack bonus +4 and every 4 points of base attack bonus thereafter.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Duelist","identifiedName":"Blooded Skeptic"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.nFtWejBuxXYpFycO"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereDuelist"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/duelist.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"xWk132Ech04de18I","name":"Heraldry","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>As long as you hold your clan, house, nation or party&#8217;s flag, members of that allegiance who can see the flag (including yourself) treat the effects of your tactics as though you had 5 additional ranks in Diplomacy. In addition, you gain a +1 bonus on all attack rolls while within the area of a tactic you create. A flag must held in either one hand or attached to a longspear, pole, or other similar object in order to grant this bonus. If the standard is taken by the enemy or destroyed, the bonuses granted by this talent become a penalty, you treat the effects of your tactics as though you had 5 less ranks in Diplomacy (to a minimum of 0), and you take a -1 penalty on all attack rolls within the area of tactics you create. This penalty lasts for 24 hours or until you repair your destroyed standard or acquire a new standard. <strong>Associated Feat:</strong> Flagbearer.</p>\n<p><strong>Special:</strong> If you have the banner class feature or other similar ability, you may treat your banner as your flag for the purposes of this talent.</p>\n<p><strong>Flag:</strong> A flag is a colorful banner that bears the heraldry or symbol of a nation or organization. A character with the Warleader (Heraldry) talent who bears a flag can grant additional combat bonuses to allies inside tactics they maintain. Carrying a flag in combat requires a free hand. <strong>Cost</strong> 10 gp <strong>Weight</strong> 3 lbs.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Warleader","identifiedName":"Heraldry"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ZL0U9IeEGjK7sm3E"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereWarleader"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/warleader.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"xe2ePACBJJEqMrvS","name":"Repositioning Strike","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You cause the target to stumble, letting you slip past them. You may immediately move up to half your movement speed as a free action, so long as you end your movement in a space adjacent to the target, and may even move through the target&#8217;s occupied space when doing so. This movement does not provoke attacks of opportunity from the target.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Exploit"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Fencing","identifiedName":"Repositioning Strike"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.MeQYD9i6WaeecXFi"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereFencing"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/fencing.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"xe2jSACTQnISkexc","name":"Marauding Monkey","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>While in this stance, whenever you successfully damage a creature with an attack action or attack of opportunity, you may choose to extend the duration of one of your active warleader abilities. If you choose an active shout, increase the duration by 1 round. If you choose an active tactic, the next time you maintain that tactic you may do so as a free action which allows you to recenter the tactic as normal. You can only extend the duration of an individual shout or tactic once per round with this talent.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Stance"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Warleader","identifiedName":"Marauding Monkey"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Z4JpuOf87NEjMHoN"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereWarleader"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/warleader.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"xiB3LWLrb1yjGmzf","name":"Dispiriting Roar","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>When you use this shout, all hostile creatures within its radius must succeed at a Will saving throw or have all morale bonuses benefiting them reduced by 1 for the shout&#8217;s duration. This is a mind-affecting fear effect. For every 4 ranks in Diplomacy you possess, the creature&#8217;s morale bonuses are reduced by an additional 1.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Shout"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Warleader","identifiedName":"Dispiriting Roar"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.KG5Rwo4Rnc9Zh3lW"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereWarleader"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/warleader.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"xknqfUZEV9zvH15p","name":"Steel Body","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>While wearing heavy armor and taking the total defense action you gain DR/bludgeoning or piercing equal to 1/2 your base attack bonus. This stacks with any DR/- you may possess.</p>\n<p><strong>Normal:</strong> Typed damage reduction does not stack with untyped damage reduction.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Equipment","identifiedName":"Steel Body"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Rom6SfVqZWMxaoHb"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereEquipment"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/equipment.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"xpBvwdZIKBi0EzgZ","name":"Grandstanding Slam","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Whenever you use a (slam) talent, you may make make an Intimidate check against all those who can see you except for the creature which was affected by the (slam) talent to demoralize them, gaining a +2 bonus on this check. For every 4 points of base attack bonus you possess, this bonus increases by +2.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Wrestling","identifiedName":"Grandstanding Slam"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.AXObhSgs20gDY1y3"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereWrestling"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/wrestling.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"xq47veXb2m0mOT0u","name":"Magic In The Spirits","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Barroom sphere, base attack bonus +4.</p>\n<p>So long as you have the drunk status, any weapon you wield gains a +1 enhancement bonus per 4 base attack bonus you possess (maximum: +5). This does not stack with any enhancement bonus the weapon might already possess. This is a supernatural effect.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Barroom","identifiedName":"Magic In The Spirits"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.dtMpzVAsvkj594bW"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereBarroom"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/barroom.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"xtjJZDa3w3aVZrnE","name":"Standardized Drones","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You can create standardized drones. Standardized drones benefit from standardized bonus hit points, natural armor bonus, and base ability scores in place of those granted by their size. Standardized drones have bonus hit points equal to 3 times their base attack bonus, and a natural armor bonus equal to half their base attack bonus.</p>\n<p>In addition standardized drones possess a base Strength and Dexterity score of 12 and increase their Strength or Dexterity by 1 for every Hit Die they possess (chosen for each Hit Die they gain). Drones created this way all have the same material cost of the largest size category you would normally be able to make regardless of their actual size.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Tech","identifiedName":"Standardized Drones"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.1qVV0ILw0smNEcsW"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereTech"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"xxVYkmNMBgDpDhH6","name":"Steal Spells","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Scoundrel sphere, Sleight of Hand 9 ranks.</p>\n<p>When performing a steal combat maneuver, rather than steal an item, you may attempt to transfer an ongoing spell effect from that target to yourself for 1 round per rank in Sleight of Hand you possess. At the end of this duration, the effect ends on yourself and returns to the creature it was stolen from. Time spent stolen still counts against the effect&#8217;s duration, and if the effect&#8217;s duration expires while it is stolen, it ends as normal. At 10 ranks in Sleight of Hand, the duration increases to 1 minute per rank you possess.</p>\n<p>This functions with spell effects with a target of &#8216;self&#8217;, but does not otherwise function with spell effects that would consider you an invalid target (for example, if the effect only targets specific creature types). This is a supernatural effect.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Trick"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"sphere":"Scoundrel","identifiedName":"Steal Spells"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.A7j6ZVOMHGT5QRKA"},"spheres-sheet":{"sphere":"SpheresSheet.SphereScoundrel"}},"img":"modules/spheres-sheet/icons/spheres/scoundrel.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"xxv3ltXwgla9EBR6","name":"Intercepting Shot","permission":{"default":0,"55oRMeK8J5d3pvei":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>As a readied action, you may attempt to shoot down a ranged attack. This does not work against unusually massive ranged weapons (such as boulders or ballista bolts, unless you are also using a massive projectile, such as a boulder or siege weapon ammunition of no more than 1 size smaller), natural attacks, or ranged attacks generated by spell effects. Make a ranged attack. If your attack roll is higher than the attack roll of the ranged attack you are intercepting, their attack is negated. You suffer a -4 penalty to this attack roll for every size category larger than you the attacker is.</p>\n<p>If you possess the Vigilant Sharpshooter talent, you may use an attack of opportunity to make an intercepting shot against a ranged attack that crosses through your threatened area.</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"0","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"combatTalent","associations":{"classes":[]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType"